{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">加深对电流表构造的理解，学会把灵敏电流计改装成电流表的方法。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">并联电路有分流作用。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电源、开关、滑动变阻器、小灯泡、电流表、灵敏电流计、定值电阻</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.将灵敏电流计与定值电阻并联后接入电路；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.闭合开关</span>S<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，观察灵敏电流计示数与电流表示数。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">给灵敏电流计并联一定阻值的电阻可以把灵敏电流计改装成一定量程的电流表。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">改装后量程与并联电阻关系：</span><em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">I</span></em></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">改</span></sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">=<em>I</em></span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">满</span></sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">+(<em>I</em></span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">满</span></sub><span style=\"color:#000000\"><em>r/R</em>)。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}